=====================================================================
  Wales Scenery 
=====================================================================

An attempt at creating South Wales scenery for flightgear.

The main area of interest initially is the M4 corridor in South Wales,
the stretch from the Severn Bridges to Swansea, and south of the M4 
motorway. Also of interest will be the Bristol Area.

=== Airports ===
* Cardiff EGLL - right next to the sea, with a railway line before 
                 the threshold, a power station, holiday resort and 
                 open cast mines nearby. Also a huge hangar at Cardiff.
* Bristol and Bristol Filton.

=== Landmarks ===
* Severn Bridge
* Second Severn Crossing
* Brunels Bridge in a gorge
* Porttalbot steelworks, power station and gas terminal
* Cardiff Bay area




